Good morning kind people!
Remember to set yourself apart from everyone else.
Schools, work, the corporate industry,
all trying to make a "default" human being.
Do, say, look and act a specific way.
People call it our inner child, I call it being yourself.
Just because you're acting differently,
doesn't make it childish.
Be you, cause there will never be another you.
.
